{
  "stem": "2735.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I should come and help out at the telegraph.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because this was organization that they had the post offices, the telephone, the telegraph-- everything under umbrella.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've never worked on a telegraph.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were giving me a crash course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was getting heart breaking telegrams from people, from soldiers, from families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I was coming home-- and my mother was worried very much that that building-- that was the nicest building in town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was made of marble or granite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a five story building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So every day was-- we were afraid to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the Wednesday-- now, that's from Sunday-- Wednesday it didn't stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean all day they were bombarding the town. 5 o'clock we were-- I went through the garden-- wanted to go over-- not to the main street, but to the side street.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was glass, and wires, and ambulances.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was dark-- I don't know, like dark from-- from smoke or from something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We went back home, and it got quiet for a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my parents said that we are not going to get undressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We're not going to sleep-- that we'll take turns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So just the children, they-- we were laying like, with the clothes, like for 1/2 an hour, an hour.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And everybody else from the neighborhood came in and was in the garden, because they probably thought because of the shrubbery and of the trees that they'll be safe.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now I learned that why was this area so heavily bombarded-- because I couldn't think of anything what we had in this area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they said that the police would not-- was just about a block away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And about 9 o'clock, they started to hit again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were in the garden.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
